$timeout.
    - used to execute user defined function after some specified time.

    Syntax.

        $timeout(my_fun , 5000);

        function my_fun(){
            //Logic Goes Here
        }


$interval
    - used to execute the function repeatedely with a given interval of time.

   Syntax.

    $interval(my_fun,1000);

    function my_fun(){
        //Logic Goes Here
    }


$location.
    - used to find the absolute path of web application.